{"tid":1360690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"促請政府唔好隊冧大嶼山","createTime":"2019-07-24T11:53:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T12:16:30.000Z","uid":284989,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"76576c8ef977936cf88ace5874e43999fbe888d8","tid":1360690,"uid":284989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:53:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">可以幫忙去簽個名嗎？我唔想見到香港得返啲石屎，唔想見到香港獨有的珍貴的海洋生物滅絕，麻煩各位去綠色和平個網頁簽個名，促請政府先發展棕地，唔好隊冧大嶼山。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://act.greenpeace.org/page/40590/petition/1?utm_campaign=2019-elm&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_content=20190530-ecology_oceans_species#/ecology\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact.greenpeace.org%2Fpage%2F40590%2Fpetition%2F1%3Futm_campaign%3D2019-elm%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_content%3D20190530-ecology_oceans_species%23%2Fecology&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9SLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=e1cedf93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act.greenpeace.org/page/40590/petition/1?utm_campaign=2019-elm&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_content=20190530-ecology_oceans_species#/ecology</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港海洋孕育近6千種海洋生物，東大嶼水域生態豐富多樣，是國家重點保護野生動物白腹海雕的繁殖及棲息地，更錄得全球獨有的鮑氏雙足蜥，附近水域亦發現稀有的軟珊瑚海筆。<br />\n<br />\n政府強推「明日大嶼」，在如此敏感的生態區域大興土木，必然破壞珍貴的海洋生態；它亦是香港史上最昂貴的基建，造價至少6,240億元，不但可能耗盡香港的財政儲備，亦無法有效解決香港的房屋問題。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，香港有比「明日大嶼」更明智的選項：我們最新的調查發現，發展棕地造價僅333億元，比填海便宜8成，卻可興建近14萬伙公營房屋。<br />\n<br />\n海洋住屋不對立，為了珍貴脆弱的海洋生態，及讓市民安居樂業，一起發聲，要求政府優先發展棕地，放棄不負責任的「明日大嶼」！"},{"pid":"5a8ce829ca342f6ba502d65824c90bf80eff05e3","tid":1360690,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:55:18.000Z","msg":"唔好意思!!<br />\n後日0726就係機場集會!!!<br />\n機場有無數外國旅客!!!<br />\n係對外發出香港嘅SOS求救訊號嘅大好機會!!!<br />\n一定要搞大佢!!!<br />\n宜家一齊推&darr;&darr;&darr;<br />\n<br />\n❲0726機場❳ 多國語言 發動全球文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[繼續開花] 到我地機師做野喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359574\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359574</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a4d1e4b80f4bc32b0bf1fe8b8e3b990820fc08eb","tid":1360690,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:00:19.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"3dcc343e02e199a3920896cf5057994f4fbcae8c","tid":1360690,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:00:34.000Z","msg":"呢個必推"},{"pid":"52dbb26439221c7a64d4a9d3adf41ded969ec287","tid":1360690,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:00:44.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"f46edb57e447baa84a4d323a7243aaa43a28f5a6","tid":1360690,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:01:50.000Z","msg":"但係簽完佢電話打黎叫我捐錢"},{"pid":"2245a45f5ee5933d3d20bc6194549abfea471efe","tid":1360690,"uid":265857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:03:56.000Z","msg":"Done,push"},{"pid":"30bd3d04385805902fde39304df8c7f34481089b","tid":1360690,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:06:51.000Z","msg":"簽左"},{"pid":"69bad3451ffedb956ef29fc76accf590fcd2e003","tid":1360690,"uid":169246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:09:32.000Z","msg":"最慘係d錢去哂d貪官到"},{"pid":"4e90268ab9f51a779287557fcd8ce0d196240a25","tid":1360690,"uid":284989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f46edb57e447baa84a4d323a7243aaa43a28f5a6","tid":1360690,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:01:50.000Z","msg":"但係簽完佢電話打黎叫我捐錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"咁奇怪？我簽完無人打比我喎！而且我今次無打算捐錢，只係覺得大嶼山太珍貴，作為香港人一定要出聲！"},{"pid":"4967cf3b5b4e1801221c8cb707587d2e68da6dda","tid":1360690,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:11:14.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"873d8fad